    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dramatic or mimic representations, usually of a light or humorous character, such as was commonly introduced between the acts of the long mystery-plays or moralities, or exhibited as part of an elaborate entertainment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
